<p>Sriram's goal in the coming years is to deploy telemedicine platforms in rural communities worldwide. He is passionate about understanding new domains, geographies, markets, cultures, and people.</p></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:39545b18 --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:68cef0a1 --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:295ad087 --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:1fa8262f --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:2e42fac6 --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:1eee059c --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:6261f07c --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:556371d9 --></div></div></div><!-- /vcwb/dynamicElementComment:70c8aeab --><!-- vcwb/dynamicElementComment:d47c5ee9 --><div class="vce-row-container" data-vce-boxed-width="true"><div class="vce-row vce-row--col-gap-30 vce-row-equal-height vce-row-content--top" id="el-d47c5ee9" data-vce-do-apply="all el-d47c5ee9"><div class="vce-row-content" data-vce-element-content="true"><!-- vcwb/dynamicElementComment:f9b1f1e2 --><div class="vce-col vce-col--md-auto vce-col--xs-1 vce-col--xs-last vce-col--xs-first vce-col--sm-last vce-col--sm-first vce-col--md-last vce-col--lg-last vce-col--xl-last vce-col--md-first vce-col--lg-first vce-col--xl-first" id="el-f9b1f1e2"><div class="vce-col-inner" data-vce-do-apply="border margin background  el-f9b1f1e2"><div class="vce-col-content" data-vce-element-content="true" data-vce-do-apply="padding el-f9b1f1e2"><!-- vcwb/dynamicElementComment:6b6f492d --><div class="vce-text-block leaderDescription"><div class="vce-text-block-wrapper vce" id="el-6b6f492d" data-vce-do-apply="all el-6b6f492d"><p>His specialities include business development, product management, telecom infrastructure (LTE, 3G, 2G, SS7, Diameter), AI and machine learning in the healthcare domain, and web development (UI/UX and backend), social, cloud, mobility and analytics.
